FBIS4-4181 "drchi083_f_94005" FBIS-CHI-94-083 Daily Report 29 Apr 1994 Near East & South Asia Luo Gan Receives Bangladesh Law Minister Luo Gan Receives Bangladesh Law Minister OW2904055094 Beijing XINHUA in English 0530 GMT 29 Apr 94 OW2904055094 Beijing XINHUA English BFN [Text] Beijing, April 29 (XINHUA) -- Luo Gan, Chinese state councillor and secretary-general of the State Council, met with Golam Hafiz, Bangladesh minister of law and justice, and his party here today. Chinese Minister of Justice Xiao yang was present at the meeting. Hafiz, also president of the Bangladesh-China Friendship Association, and his party are here as guests of the Chinese People's Association for Friendship With Foreign Countries.
